      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="96.34.1_2_0059"/>Hrn Dr. Robert Adam,</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb62" type="place">Wien XII</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb1239" type="place">Meidlinger Hauptstr 56</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="96.34.1_2_0060"/><rs type="work" ref="#pmb298283"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168815">Wien, XVIII, Sternwartestr. 71</rs>.</hi></rs></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="96.34.1_2_0059"/><date>9. X. 1916</date>.</dateline><salute>Verehrter Herr Doktor,</salute></opener><p>vielen Dank für Ihren Brief. Seit <date>30. Sept.</date> bin ich wieder daheim. Pa<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t
               es Ihnen, schon <date>Do<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>er<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag (12.)</date> gegen <time><hi rend="underline" n="1">7</hi> Abends</time><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>eien Sie mir willko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en!</p><closer>Herzlich grüßen<unclear>d</unclear><lb/>Ihr ergebner<lb/><signed>ArthurSchnitzler</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
